title: Rachel Rising, Volume 5: Night Cometh
description: Rachel, Jet, and Aunt Johnny recover quickly from their harrowing adventures with the aid of a magic herbal wrap, but they soon discover they've been the victims of a serial killer. Now they are determined to find the mysterious predator and deliver him to the evil of Zoe's knife. This new book is the 5th trade paperback in Terry Moore's Eisner Award nominated series, collecting issues #25-30.
author: Terry Moore
